scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Hey, April!

scenes.name: April
scenes.text: Hi, dad!

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: I don't know who that was, but there may be more.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Maybe you should stay up here for a while.

scenes.name: April
scenes.text: Sure!

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Hey, Sarah!

scenes.name: Sarah
scenes.text: Are you alright?

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Yes, I'm not sure about the other guy though.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: I'm going to go check for more.

scenes.name: Sarah
scenes.text: I'll come with you.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Thanks! I would prefer if you stay here withApril though.

scenes.name: Sarah
scenes.text: If you insist. Be careful!

scenes.name: Skipper
scenes.text: It's too soon!

scenes.name: Turnerr
scenes.text: What?

scenes.name: Skipper
scenes.text: Oh, hi, Turner!

scenes.name: Skipper
scenes.text: Maybe you should go check if there are any otherraider scouts.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: That's my plan; aren't you coming?

scenes.name: Skipper
scenes.text: Me? Oh, uh, no. I have to... defend this area.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Ah, true. Take care of my family!

scenes.name: Skipper
scenes.text: Don't worry, I will.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Hey, Jack######!

scenes.name: Jack###
scenes.text: Hey, what's up?

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: I think I may have just found a raider scout.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: I'm going to look for more. will you come with me?

scenes.name: Jack###
scenes.text: I would, but I hurt my feet yesterday when I fell offthe lookout ruins.

scenes.name: Jack###
scenes.text: I'm not as agile as I used to be.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Ah, ok. Please look after my family!

scenes.name: Jack###
scenes.text: I will!

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Hey, you're awake!

scenes.name: Clover#
scenes.text: I am! What happened over there?

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: A stranger attacked me, I don't know why.

scenes.name: Clover#
scenes.text: Oh god, that's how it began...

scenes.name: Clover#
scenes.text: We have to leave.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Huh?

scenes.name: Clover#
scenes.text: No, it couldn't have been real. Never mind.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Ok. I'll talk to you later!

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: What do you think you're doing here?

scenes.name: Wanderer
scenes.text: Hey now, is this how you greet all visitors?

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: No, but I met one a few minutes ago who attacked mewithout warning!

scenes.name: Wanderer
scenes.text: What? The raiders are coming here too?

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: So that WAS a raider scout!

scenes.name: Wanderer
scenes.text: Come with me, I can help you.
